author: jeremy_a
msg: Refactor the JDBC connection pool to make it easier to support new implementations of the pool.
Reimplement the JMeter 1.9-style pool to match this new interface.
Fix the hashCode/equals implementations in DBKey.
Make it possible to use two JDBCSamplers with the same URL but different username/password.

author: jeremy_a
msg: Removed the readObject and writeObject methods, as they were just calling the defaultRead/WriteObject methods.
